room_title: Escape room "Embalming Room Zombie Escape" by Mystere Escape Rooms in New Orleans
room_description: Hidden in the room is the key to escape protected by a chained up bloodthirsty Zombie. Zombie's chain grows longer as your hour ticks away, so hurry up and find a way out of here before you are contaminated! You have 60 minutes to uncover the clues, decipher riddles, unlock the door and escape the room without being touched!
